    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it is spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a dream car that\u2019s basically perfect, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43800.0,
