    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2014 Porsche 911 Carrera S, featuring the legendary 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six engine. This S-trim variant delivers 400hp with a linear power band and a visceral acoustic profile. The 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transaxle provides instantaneous gear synchronization, complemented by Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV) and a mechanical rear-axle differential lock for optimized lateral dynamics. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), lowering the ride height by 10mm for superior roll stiffness. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero evidence of bore scoring, no thermal cycling fatigue on the exhaust manifolds, and factory-spec compression across all cylinders. The undercarriage is immaculate, with all bushings and seals retaining their original elasticity. A turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
