    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did on the dealership floor. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish, and has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery remains firm and uncreased, and the interior still carries a faint new-car aroma. Every button, screen, and mechanical component operates with precision. It has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. Accompanied by a full, meticulous service history from certified specialists, this car represents the pinnacle of its model for a discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
